Here are the recent updates to http://awk.info .

(For all updates to awk.info, subscribe to
http://tinyurl.com/rss4awk. To contribute to awk.info,
see http://awk.info/?contribute .)

-----------------------------------------------------------
TOOLS

Tim Menzies offers a (very) simple RSS reader.
- http://awk.info/?tools/rss

Debbie Forbes quickly sorts arrays.
- http://awk.info/?tools/o

Peter Ivanyi and Roman Putanowicz generated Latex doco
from program comments.
- http://awk.info/?tools/adoc

Dan Nielsen's shows us how to draw Sierpinski Triangles.
- http://awk.info/?wst

Ed Morton and Kenny McCormack show us Awk's 
equivalent to VI's "J" command.
- http://awk.info/?j

-----------------------------------------------------------
